title: Borderline V1-V4 (2006-2011) (digital Empire)cbz
description:
Story and art by Chris Trillo and Eduardo Risso. Translated by Ivan Brandon. Originally published in Italy, Borderline is a 600-page epic created by Risso and writer Chris Trillo. Described by Harvey and Eisner Award-winning creator Risso as a 'sci-fi, post-apocalyptic story that openly shows the miseries and kindness of Humankind,' Borderline is available for the first time in English from Dynamite Entertainment! Foreword by writer and collaborator Brian (Superman, 100 Bullets) Azzarello!
